          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurement of the E(c.m.)=184 keV Resonance Strength",
                " in the 26gAl(p,gamma)27Si Reaction"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "FRS"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANTMF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " the DRAGON recoil separator in the ISAC",
                " radioactive ion beam facility at TRIUMF."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A high-power SiC target was bombarded with up to 70",
                " microA of 500 MeV protons from TRIUMF's sector",
                " focussing cyclotron, producing radioactive 26gAl"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BGO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The DRAGON facility consists of a windowless",
                " hydrogen-recirculating gas target surrounded by an",
                " array of 30 bismuth germanate (BGO) detectors, and a",
                " two-stage electromagnetic recoil separator."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The total separator length from the center of",
                " the gas cell to the final m=q focus is 20.42 m, with",
                " a double-sided silicon strip detector (DSSD) placed",
                " 65 cm downstream from the focus. A collimated silicon",
                " surface barrier detector placed at 30 degree from the",
                " center of the gas cell was used to detect protons",
                " elastically scattered by the incoming beam during the",
                " run as a means of normalization."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A gas-target pressure of 6 Torr was maintained to",
                " within +/- 1.6%."
              ]
            }
          ],
